                                    rel="noopener">Source</a></p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                        <div class="iot-gathers-massive-img-point">
                            <div class="iot-gathers-massive-img img-row-sample healthcare-applications-img02"></div>
                            <p>63% of health care organizations will invest more than $1 million in 2019. <a
